{{doc/start}}
Lua module that renders visual recipe cards showing inputs, outputs, base craft time, and per-building throughput rates. Called by [[Template:RecipeCard]], [[Template:RecipeCard Building]], and [[Template:RecipeCard Recipe]].

Each card uses a two-section layout: a summary section (inputs → outputs flow + base time) and a rate section listing per-building craft times and items/minute rates with <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> tooltips.

== Data sources ==

{| class="wikitable"
! Module !! Used for
|-
| [[Module:Data/Recipes]] || Recipe inputs, outputs, base craft time
|-
| [[Module:Data/RecipeIndex]] || Maps item/element identifiers to recipe identifiers (by input or output)
|-
| [[Module:Data/BuildingRecipeIndex]] || Maps building identifiers to lists of recipe identifiers
|-
| [[Module:Data/RecipeCraftingData]] || Per-building craft times, used to compute throughput rates
|-
| [[Module:Data/Items]] || Resolving item display names
|-
| [[Module:Data/Elements]] || Resolving element display names
|-
| [[Module:Data/Buildings]] || Resolving building display names
|}

All data modules are auto-generated by <code>foundry_parser generate-lua</code>. Do not edit them directly.

== Exported functions ==

=== <code>p.main(frame)</code> ===
Renders one or more recipe cards for an item or element. Called by [[Template:RecipeCard]].

{| class="wikitable"
! Argument !! Description !! Status
|-
| <code>id</code> / <code>1</code> || Item or element template identifier || Required
|-
| <code>mode</code> || <code>producing</code> (default), <code>consuming</code>, or <code>all</code> || Optional
|}

=== <code>p.building(frame)</code> ===
Renders recipe cards for all recipes craftable in a building. Called by [[Template:RecipeCard Building]].

{| class="wikitable"
! Argument !! Description !! Status
|-
| <code>id</code> / <code>1</code> || Building template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_assembler_i</code>) || Required
|}

=== <code>p.recipe(frame)</code> ===
Renders a single recipe card by recipe identifier. Called by [[Template:RecipeCard Recipe]].

{| class="wikitable"
! Argument !! Description !! Status
|-
| <code>id</code> / <code>1</code> || Recipe template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_conveyor_i</code>) || Required
|}

== Notes ==
* Per-building throughput rates are computed as <code>(amount / craft_time_seconds) × 60</code> to give items/minute.
* Rates are rounded to integers where possible; otherwise displayed to 2 decimal places.
* Elemental inputs/outputs (fluids, gases) are shown with a litre (<code>L</code>) unit suffix.
* The "Hand" crafting entry is displayed as plain text rather than a building link.
* Cards are styled via <code>Template:RecipeCard/styles.css</code>.
* If no recipes match, the function returns an empty string.
